5:
Myaah! Mew-Mew had a blast
today! Flashy New Year's festivals
are the best!
12:
Are they tops? Myreowr... What
pretty patterns...
16:
Those are traditional toys from
Yamato. I hear they have a custom
of spinning them for the new year.
21:
Oh yeah. I got them as holiday
presents. Want to give them a whirl?
27: Mew-Mew would love to! Thank you!
32: I wouldn't mind a spin myself.
41:
Heh-heh! Now, let's see who can
keep the top spinning fur the
longest!
45:
You woke me up from my nap for
THIS?
49:
Myeh-heh-heh... Mew're just a
scaredy cat, afraid mew'll lose the
contest. Guess mew're gonna
chicken out?
53:
Scaredy cat? CHICKEN?! Those are
fighting words! Hyaaah!
56:
Myahah! Mew-Mew knew Nimbus
would chew-chew the bait!
61:
Well, what are we just standing
around for? Let's spin.
66:
Myaaah, they're so colorful and
pretty...
68:
They're just as cute as Mew-Mew's
outfit—she loves Yamato!
75: I think I needed more leverage.
80: Um, Mew, whatever is the matter?
85:
Watching them go spin-spin... It's
making Mew-Mew's paws itch!
Myoh-oh-oh!
99:
Myaaargh, Mew-Mew's sorry! Her
body doesn't listen so well!
103:
Ahaha! It's okay, Mew. Now, let's try
one more time...
111:
Myuh?! Mew-Mew's paws are
moving on their own! Are her
beastfolk instincts finally kicking in?!
114:
Myaha! This puts Mew-Mew one
step closer to being a complete kitty
cat!
121:
Keep spinning, everyone! With every
meowtation, Mew-Mew feels her
bestial nature growing!
124:
What happened to the competition?
You were the one who forced us into
this.
127:
That's not what's important right
now.
131:
You've got a lot of nerve, you know
that?
143:
Mwahaha! Round and round we go!
Mwahaha!
147:
Something tells me we should
probably stop now.
151:
Mwaaah, that was bundles of fun!
Thanks, everrrybody!
154: Um, all we did was spin tops...
158:
No, mew all did much more. Ever
since meeting mew, my days have
been filled with excitement!
160:
So thank mew all for always sticking
by Mew-Mew!
162:
Mew-Mew promises to be the very
best frrriend she can be to you all!
167:
The same. It is our honor to have
you as an ally.
172:
In that case, Mew-Mew has
something to add to her
competition with Nimbus!
176:
She promises that, this year, she's
gonna become a beastfolk warrior
even stronger and meaner than him!
180:
Hah. I'll take you up on that
challenge. Just don't get cold paws
like you did back on that stage.
183:
Mew-Mew's claws are all warmed
up now!
187:
Ah, but Mew-Mew almost forgot to
say the most important thing!
190:
Happy Mew Year, everyone! Let's
make it the best year ever!
